<li><a href="http://www.fda.gov/OHRMS/DOCKETS/98fr/02n-0475-n000001.pdf" target="_blank">OHRP/HHS Draft "Financial Relationships and Interests in Research Involving Human Subjects: Guidance for Human Subject Protection"</a>(April 2003)</li>
<li><a href="http://grants.nih.gov/grants/guide/notice-files/NOT-OD-00-040.html" target="_blank">"Financial Conflicts of Interest and Research Objectivity: Issues for Investigators and Institutional Review Boards", NIH Guide.</a> (June 5, 2000)</li>
<li><a href="http://grants.nih.gov/grants/policy/coifaq.htm" target="_blank">Frequently asked questions Concerning the Department of Health and Human Services Objectivity in Research Regulations and the National Science Foundation Investigator Financial Disclosure Policy.</a> (July 3,1996)</li>
